The paper focuses on vision-and-language reasoning, which involves understanding both visual concepts and language semantics and their alignment. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR). Among these, cs.CL and cs.CV are the most likely categories, as the paper specifically deals with the intersection of these two fields.
